    • Method Detail

      • parseSamples

        public void parseSamples()
                  throws Exception
        Parse all RdpClassifier reports in the input directory.
        Build an RdpNode for each line.
        If isValid(OtuNode),
        1. Create ParsedSample for the OtuNodeImpl.getSampleId() if not yet created.
        2. Add the OtuNodeImpl.getCount() (1) to ParsedSample OTU count.

        Sample QIIME report line (head 7A_1_reported.tsv):
        FCABK7W:1:2105:21787:12788#/1 Root rootrank 1.0 Bacteria domain 1.0 Firmicutes phylum 1.0 Clostridia class 1.0 Clostridiales order 1.0 Ruminococcaceae family 1.0 Faecalibacterium genus 1.0

        Specified by:
        parseSamples in interface ParserModule
        Specified by:
        parseSamples in class ParserModuleImpl
        Throws:
        Exception - if error occurs while parsing classifier reports
